126
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:18,207
Well, that sounds like
an incredible opportunity.

127
00:08:18,290 --> 00:08:19,291
Thank you.

128
00:08:20,792 --> 00:08:21,960
I just...

129
00:08:22,044 --> 00:08:24,004
